title: Spaghetti Bolognese
instructions: Cook spaghetti. Cook ground beef. Mix with tomato sauce.

title: Veggie Stir Fry
instructions: Stir fry vegetables. Add soy sauce.

title: Chicken Tikka Masala
ingredients: chicken breasts, yogurt, tomato paste, spices
instructions: Marinate chicken in yogurt and spices. Grill and simmer in tomato sauce.

title: Caprese Salad
ingredients: tomatoes, fresh mozzarella, basil, olive oil
instructions: Slice tomatoes and mozzarella. Arrange with basil leaves. Drizzle with olive oil.

title: Beef Tacos
ingredients: ground beef, taco seasoning, tortillas, lettuce, tomato, cheese
instructions: Cook ground beef with taco seasoning. Fill tortillas with beef and toppings.

title: Pasta Carbonara
instructions: Cook spaghetti. Fry bacon. Mix with eggs and parmesan cheese.

title: Mushroom Risotto
ingredients: arborio rice, mushrooms, onion, garlic, broth, parmesan cheese
instructions: Saute mushrooms, onion, and garlic. Cook rice with broth. Stir in parmesan cheese.

title: Thai Green Curry
ingredients: chicken, green curry paste, coconut milk, bell peppers, bamboo shoots
instructions: Cook chicken with green curry paste. Add coconut milk, bell peppers, and bamboo shoots.

title: Vegetable Pizza
ingredients: pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, bell peppers, mushrooms, olives
instructions: Spread tomato sauce on pizza dough. Add toppings and cheese. Bake until crust is golden.

title: Greek Salad
ingredients: cucumbers, tomatoes, red onion, feta cheese, olives, olive oil
instructions: Chop vegetables and feta cheese. Toss with olives and olive oil.

title: Beef Wellington
ingredients: beef tenderloin, mushrooms, puff pastry, prosciutto, egg yolk
instructions: Sear beef. Spread with mushroom duxelles. Wrap in puff pastry with prosciutto. Bake until golden.

title: Pad Thai
ingredients: rice noodles, shrimp, tofu, peanuts, bean sprouts, tamarind sauce
instructions: Soak noodles. Stir fry shrimp and tofu. Add noodles, peanuts, bean sprouts, and tamarind sauce.

title: Ratatouille
ingredients: eggplant, zucchini, bell peppers, tomatoes, onion, garlic, herbs
instructions: Slice and saute vegetables. Layer in baking dish. Bake until tender.

title: Sushi Rolls
ingredients: sushi rice, nori seaweed, raw fish or vegetables, soy sauce, wasabi, pickled ginger
instructions: Prepare sushi rice. Roll with fish or vegetables in seaweed. Slice and serve with soy sauce, wasabi, and ginger.

title: Tiramisu
ingredients: ladyfingers, espresso, mascarpone cheese, cocoa powder, rum
instructions: Soak ladyfingers in espresso. Layer with mascarpone mixture. Dust with cocoa powder. Chill before serving.
